name: A Memory of What It Felt Like
description:
Thunderstorm rages in Jakarta sky. A depiction of one’s feelings at a certain period. Digitally produced.  

A transformative take on a photo by Indro Muktiono. The original photo might be included as a part of a future photo collection.

Jakarta, September 21, 2021.
 3240 × 2160 seamlessly looping cinemagraph in MP4 format.
